      "description": "An exceptional driver\u2019s specimen, this 997-generation 911 Carrera features the revered 3.6L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque and a visceral soundtrack. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, mechanical throws, paired with a clutch that retains excellent take-up feel. This unit benefits from a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed cooling system to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited drives. The suspension geometry remains dialed, providing the communicative front-end bite and rear-engine traction characteristic of the marque. Cosmetically honest for its mileage, it remains mechanically robust, featuring ventilated rotors with four-piston monobloc calipers that provide firm, consistent pedal pressure. A purist-spec machine optimized for corner-exit stability and tactile feedback.",
